PrecisRegulations Amending the FEDERAL AUTHORITIES REGULATIONS by placing the Canada-Nova Scotia Offshore Petroleum Board on the list of federal authorities who are required to carry out an environmental assessment of any project that is to be undertaken on federal lands before selling, leasing or otherwise disposing of any interest in those lands.
